{"tid":2005510,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"柯宇綸: 《色，戒》片酬低過香港電影","createTime":"2020-05-07T06:57:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T18:16:05.000Z","uid":134071,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"04a32ee6d15580466861e2fc43cc2405236ecbac","tid":2005510,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:57:04.000Z","msg":"柯宇綸因為支持「太陽花運動」, 被中共封殺, 大家真係要支持佢. (而且佢係影片開頭都講粵語)<br />\n<br />\n柯宇綸話佢演出由王晶監製的香港電影《愈快樂愈墮落》, 片酬有40萬台幣.<br />\n<br />\n反而, 柯宇綸係幾年後演出李安導演《色，戒》, 套戲拍左八個月, 但片酬只有20萬台幣. (雖然劇組係每個拍攝日都向柯宇綸給予100港元的膳食費.) 但柯宇綸唔後悔, 因為可以換到八個月時間向李安學者.<br />\n<br />\n柯宇綸話佢近年試過收過百萬台幣片酬. (我估計是指大陸合拍片《風再起時》....套片<br />\n因為有柯宇綸, 過唔到大陸審查, 正在被雪藏中.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAH7B_sOL-c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaAH7B_sOL-c&d=w9JnFmhD9tlFtzSpwKDBdfFndj8FUwf2P%2BvTNEmbS2k%3D&h=71074995\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aAH7B_sOL-c</a>"},{"pid":"4a921432db86d6ad66f7fd0f99ff15a698b5957a","tid":2005510,"uid":134071,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T06:58:32.000Z","msg":"拍攝八個月, 收20萬台幣片酬, 相信而家大部分演員都唔肯. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e8a82747021eeb6d5c64f0dcdfef587e9809233","tid":2005510,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"李安呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24f9f51f2481d918bf52d2b3c3d558f412f1e9c4","tid":2005510,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e8a82747021eeb6d5c64f0dcdfef587e9809233","tid":2005510,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:00:38.000Z","msg":"李安呀...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-07T07:03:28.000Z","msg":"時勢唔同<br />\n<br />\n王家衛都開始被